description: Easy vegetarian shakshuka, great as a side or on its own.
keywords: Shakshuka,Seafood free,Wheat free,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Sesame free,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Shakshuka with Vegetables Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 34 tbs moroccan seasoning ( add to your desired taste)

recipeInstructions.text: Combine zucchini, capsicum, onion and garlic in a sheet pan or large rectangular oven proof dish, drizzle with olive oil and toss to coat.
In a mixing bowl, combine tinned tomato, tomato paste and Moroccan seasoning. Stir to combine then pour over veggie mix and toss to coat well.
Roast in oven for 35 mins then remove from oven.
Using the back of a spoon, make 6 evenly spaced dents in your veggie mix. Break 1 egg into each dent, sprinkle with salt and pepper
Return to oven for 710 mins or until eggs are cooked as desired. Remove from oven and sprinkle a little parsley on top.
